While it would be great if PoP has good control environments, not everyone will be raiding PoP exclusively, people will still want to raid things in Velious and Luclin. Since it seems quite unlikely for Verant to retune all the old encounters so that enchanters have something useful to do most of the time, the only thing to fix us in old content is the spell lineup. The jury is obviously still out on whether or not the 60+ mezzes and charms will allow enchanters to participate in content they previously could not... but the assumption is that they won't be allowed, or quickly nerfed once PoP is out, meaning that Insanity is the <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> only</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> thing on the spell list that could allow the (second) enchanter in velious and much of luclin to be useful.<br>
<br>
